{"tid":1740883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"12月日程表 2019沒有聖誕","createTime":"2019-11-20T05:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T06:02:44.000Z","uid":189799,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2af2db9dfe39c26e2df566585889d4be15183a27","tid":1740883,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:58:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2019沒有聖誕</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zDEoLh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zDEoLh.jpg&h=093f8cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足打生打死，有人死，有人傷，有人坐梗。你地唔係仲有心情慶祝聖誕呀？<br />\n<br />\n而且，12月係重要嘅銷售月份。為左貫徹我地嘅攬炒精神。請12月盡量唔好消費。活動詳情如下:<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔好買聖誕禮物，將買聖誕禮物嘅錢捐出去。例如星火，杏林，守護孩子等等。留意番，可以順便cut埋NGO嘅捐款，因為佢地唔會幫香港人。<br />\n<br />\n2. 商場只行唔買。12月一定有好多sales，麻煩大家除生活必需品外，一律唔好買野。<br />\n<br />\n3. 黃色經濟圈宜家成熟左好多。希望大家再盡力啲拒絕藍店。唔搭黨鐵，唔用八達通，食野之前上網搵下黃店。影響埋身邊嘅朋友。"},{"pid":"261cdb43921120b6f2b464a2529865e0f9fc33d3","tid":1740883,"uid":65353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"日程唔好唔記得黎明行動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4S9LP9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4S9LP9.png&h=89dad0e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"926f3282621014c44d45dac969e413e739b98bd0","tid":1740883,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"silent night ain't silent<br />\nmerry x'mas ain't merry<br />\nhappy new year ain't happy<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1441bab2c59fb6d3b68a9ca71d36fbe0dc0443","tid":1740883,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:01:21.000Z","msg":"12月聖誕節最佳日程就係黃色經濟圈<br />\n和理非冇藉口唔支持"},{"pid":"4c9a50217a62da4987f3cca329a5873678911e1c","tid":1740883,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"法案在參議院通過咗，大家快啲去多謝議員啦！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740143</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=ea92b96c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"}]}